{"tid":1467412,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"帶動分化同割蓆既其中一個文字措辭既語氣","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:16:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:37:59.000Z","uid":202592,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2ce2fbe600c23c7b6d879ce43da2351dd9e10db6","tid":1467412,"uid":202592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:16:53.000Z","msg":"相信各位巴絲睇到一大堆唔同意見直接飛埋黎，對情緒影響好大，各位手足對今日既行動有好多唔同意見，但文字上既語氣真係好需要大家既禮貌。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「又話不分化，不割蓆，而家阻到遊客就屌晒鬼」<br />\n相信以上例子出現係好多POST到。<br />\n<br />\n好多巴打都開過POST話比意見同割蓆係完全兩回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係當措辭上既分別，就極容易引起唔同人既誤會，睇睇以下例子：<br />\n<br />\n例子1:<br />\n「屌你老母咪撚塞住D遊客啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，阻到人又無撚用，唔係話你地係鬼，但唔該真係比少少腦，<span style=\"color: red;\">塞遊客係下策黎，BLAH BLAH BLAH... </span>利申：不分化不割蓆」<br />\n<br />\n「今日見到好多義士主動塞住遊客離港，好多謝大家既行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，而家行動完左同大家分析少少利弊。<span style=\"color: red;\"> 個人認為覺得人少主動塞遊客離港都係BLAH BLAH BLAH...</span>」<br />\n<br />\n例子2:<br />\n「屌你又話要塞爆機場，而家有義士去塞遊客就屌晒鬼咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，仲話好意思不割蓆不分化。<span style=\"color: red;\">而家塞住遊客機場可以XXX</span>」<br />\n<br />\n「今日好多手足辛苦左成日，為左塞爆機場出好多力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，希望大家明白<span style=\"color: red;\">塞住遊客可以令到XXX</span>」<br />\n<br />\n<strong>紅字先係成段文字入面最重要既內容。如果各位巴絲真係希望傳達自己意見比其他人，保持好既禮貌非常重要。原因係:</strong><br />\n1. 可以減少其他巴絲既負面情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 更容易令其他人接受之後既內容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所以就算心入面屌晒鬼都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，虛偽少少多加幾句禮貌說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>，除左提高討論既氣氛，令到大家情緒更加正面，更加有助去交流意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無論係有任何既意見，希望咁多位巴絲開每個POST，每個回覆都盡量保持多D禮貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋唔好咁容易望到其他揩辭強硬既發言，就比佢影響到自己都開始屌人老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"258ef5f96388335fd926f1dd25c02cc261c75f86","tid":1467412,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:19:12.000Z","msg":"或加Li乜s達<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c03c7d4bd9b8dbee21044d56c8417889103022ec","tid":1467412,"uid":263809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:37:59.000Z","msg":"禮貌係一種有力武器"}]}